name: Evil Eye Cross Necklace in Gold
description:
Eyes are very big in fashion right now, but they also hold a lot of spiritual significance in some cultures.

The third eye (also known as the inner eye) is a mystical and esoteric concept referring to a speculative invisible eye which provides perception beyond ordinary sight. In certain dharmic spiritual traditions such as Hinduism, the third eye refers to the ajna, or brow, chakra. In New Age spirituality, people who have the capacity to utilize their third eyes are sometimes known as seers.

Each Evil Eye Cross necklace comes with a 24" metal chain that is lead- and nickel-free.
